  ('optometrist-moex-00309', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-b0a2f330', 'sub-optometrist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '上方象限視野缺損（pieinthesky）通常與視路徑的那一部分病變有關？', '["視神經", "視交叉", "頂葉的視放射", "顳葉的視放射"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "87d2d58d5233", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d9cba2739812", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0901", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼球解剖生理學與倫理法規", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00310', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-b0a2f330', 'sub-optometrist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於淚液系統的敘述，下列何者正確？①淚腺被上眼瞼提肌（levatorpalpebraesuperioris）的腱膜分為', '["Hasner瓣膜（valveofHasner）分 布在總淚管（commoncanaliculus）和淚囊（lacrimalsac）之間，防止淚液回流至總淚管", "淚腺的血 液是由淚動脈（lacrimal artery）供應", "鼻淚管（nasolacrimal duct）的開口是位在下鼻道（inferior meatus），將淚液流入鼻腔", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "87d2d58d5233", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d9cba2739812", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0901", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼球解剖生理學與倫理法規", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00311', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-b0a2f330', 'sub-optometrist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關眼眶及鼻竇之敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["眼眶的底層包含三塊骨頭：顎骨（palatine）、顴骨（zygoma）及上頜骨（maxilla），在眼眶的底層下 方是上頜竇（maxillarysinus）", "淚囊（lacrimalsac）位在淚窩（lacrimalfossa）上，淚窩由淚骨（lacrimalbone）及上頜骨所組成", "眼眶的內側壁包含篩骨（ethmoid）、淚骨及上頜骨。篩骨非常薄，炸出性骨折（blow-outfracture） 最常見的骨折處在眼眶內壁", "篩竇感染可能造成眼窩感染，感染有可能藉由眼眶靜脈（orbitalvein）進入腦部"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "87d2d58d5233", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d9cba2739812", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0901", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼球解剖生理學與倫理法規", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00312', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-b0a2f330', 'sub-optometrist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '眶下裂（inferiororbitalfissure）是由那些骨構成？①額骨（frontalbone）  ②淚骨（lacrimalbone）', '["蝶骨（sphenoidbone）", "上頜骨（maxillarybone）  ⑤顴骨（zygomaticbone）  ⑥篩骨（ethmoidbone）", "", "⑥"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "87d2d58d5233", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d9cba2739812", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0901", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼球解剖生理學與倫理法規", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00313', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-113-b0a2f330', 'sub-optometrist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於角膜構造與神經分布之敘述，下列何者正確？①角膜感覺神經來自顏面神經（facialnerve）的', '["正常老年人角膜每平方釐米有20,000個（20,000cells/mm2） 角膜內皮細胞（endothelialcells）", "角膜內皮細胞呈現不間斷五邊形排列（pentagonalarray）", "角膜平均厚度約520-550 μm，越往周邊越厚  ⑤德士密氏膜（Descemet''smembrane）會隨年紀增 加而增厚", ""]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:40+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "87d2d58d5233", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d9cba2739812", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "109", "s": "0901", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼球解剖生理學與倫理法規", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL)
